@@TJvRestartDlg
Description:
This component is an interface for the built in windows dialog asking the system to reboot. The user can choose the type of reboot he wants. (Same as Start Menu/Sutdown).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvRestartDlg.Execute
Description:
Call this method to display the dialog. if the user clicks the ok button, the system will automatically reboot, restart or shutdown.

